(64, '1670247648982x377149693685661700', '', '', '', 'How Can the Marketplace Strengthen Your Business?', 'Sometimes enterprises doubt whether it’s worth creating a marketplace to grow their business. Here are some benefits you get:\n\n[color=#808080][size=4]Diversification of the Company’s Activities[/size][/color]\n\nIf you provide services of some kind, a marketplace can be an opportunity to enter a new market. Moreover, it’s possible to attract contractors with new skills that will take your company to a new level.\n\n[color=#808080][size=4]Increase of Your Contractor Base[/size][/color]\n\nWith a marketplace, it will be much easier to boost your contractor base. You make it possible for professionals to join your marketplace and offer their services. Thus, you create a team of specialists who have a lot to propose to your clients.\n\n[color=#808080][size=4]Expansion of the Offer for Customers[/size][/color]\n\nWith a variety of experts registered in the marketplace, you have more choices for your clients. They have more options to agree upon the price or select the format of work. A vital filter can be a geographical location or a specific qualification of the expert.\n\n[color=#808080][size=4]Extension of the Services Range[/size][/color]\n\nThe marketplace is a perfect instrument for enlarging the scope of your services. On the one hand, you retain your steady customers by presenting new benefits. On the other hand, it will be easier to reach a different target audience, increasing your customer base.\n\n[color=#808080][size=4]Sale of Additional Services[/size][/color]\n\nSuppose that you offer particular services to your clients. It’s possible to create a marketplace in the neighboring segment. It will be a perfect platform for selling the company’s primary services. \nWant to know how it works? The following marketplace can be an excellent example. The main services are weight loss courses, as well as nutrition plans. Yet, the clients can also find proper fitness outfits and equipment. Moreover, personal coaching sessions are also available.\nObviously, any business wins from having a marketplace. It’s a great opportunity to expand your activity and increase profit.\nHave you determined all the parameters for your marketplace and the target audience? The Swiftle team is ready to help you develop a unique platform with awesome functionality. Let your customers or businesses you work with enjoy all the personalized benefits you offer.', 'Dec 5, 2022 3:40 pm', 'Dec 5, 2022 3:46 pm'),
